comments: First off: babe. I am a junior now and she is by far the hottest teacher I have ever had (not that that says a whole lot). Oh, and she teaches psychology pretty well. Tread carefully, however, as she is a feminist and definitely picks favorites.

She is so down to earth and nice. She makes class fun and theres never homework. Very easy to talk to very young but knows everything about psychology. Definitely recommend her to everyone. She\'s funny too
